iana.encoding_considerations:
Security considerations: This format provides no cryptographic 
   integrity or confidentiality/privacy protections of any kind. This 
   format doesn't have executable/active content, however it can be 
   used to compress executable/active content.

Interoperability considerations: At publication of this document, 
   there exists only a single reference implementation.

Published specification: None. See 
   https://github.com/kspalaiologos/bzip3 for a free and open-source, 
   LGPL v3-licensed reference implementation.

Applications which use this media: Applications that want to compress 
   data.

Fragment identifier considerations: None

Restrictions on usage: None
